Questions:
Which of the following components of the Bright IDEAS-Young Adults study is considered experimental?
A) Completing online surveys about your experiences as a young adult with cancer;
B) Receiving a list of resources for young adults with cancer;
C) Participating in six 45-minute problem-solving skills training sessions with a trained interventionist;
D) Continuing to receive usual psychosocial care available to you.

Correct answer: C
